semplice-openbox-default-settings (2.10.0) pulse; urgency=low

  * Initial pulse release.
  * panel/:
    - removed: we do not ship fbpanel anymore.
  * semplice-openbox-autostart: simplified, removed modes (only geeky remains),
    configurable panel, configurable panel configuration, pcmanfm desktop
    support, volume control can be disabled, removed xcompmgr references,
    added live-relevant settings.
  * openbox/:
    - autostart.sh: renamed to autostart, removed live-relevant section,
                    changed interval to 0.5, updated settings.
    - removed xdg-menu.py and places.sh.
  * tint2rc: ship to /etc/xdg/tint2/semplice.tint2rc.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Thu, 12 Jan 2012 21:25:58 +0100

